parameters.description: Log of maximum phytoplankton specific uptake rate mu_max (day^-1). Typical values 0.1–1.5 day^-1 depending on taxa and conditions.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log max phytoplankton specific uptake rate (day^-1)

parameters.description: Log of half-saturation constant for nutrient uptake (K_N). Controls nutrient limitation strength.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log half-saturation constant for nutrient uptake (g C m^-3)

parameters.description: Log of self-shading coefficient linking phytoplankton biomass to light limitation (larger values imply stronger light limitation).
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log self-shading coefficient for phytoplankton light limitation (m^3 gC^-1)

parameters.description: Log of maximum zooplankton ingestion rate (grazing) per unit Z biomass (day^-1).
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log max zooplankton ingestion rate per biomass (day^-1)

parameters.description: Log of phytoplankton half-saturation for grazing response (K_P).
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log phytoplankton half-saturation for grazing (g C m^-3)

parameters.description: Log of (h - 1) where h is the generalized Holling exponent; h = 1 + exp(log_h_minus1) spans Type II (near 1) to Type III (>=2).
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log of (Holling exponent minus one), h ≥ 1 dimensionless

parameters.description: Log of smooth grazing threshold concentration P_star; below this, grazing is strongly reduced.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log smooth grazing threshold phytoplankton concentration (g C m^-3)

parameters.description: Log of steepness parameter k_thr controlling how quickly grazing turns on around P_star.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log steepness of grazing threshold onset ((g C m^-3)^-1)

parameters.description: Log of phytoplankton linear mortality rate (day^-1).

parameters.description: Log of zooplankton linear mortality rate (day^-1).
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log zooplankton linear mortality rate (day^-1)

parameters.description: Logit of phytoplankton carbon-use efficiency (fraction of uptake retained as biomass). Prior mean ~0.6.

parameters.description: Logit of zooplankton assimilation efficiency (fraction of ingestion converted to Z). Prior mean ~0.3.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Logit zooplankton assimilation efficiency (fraction 0–1)
